{"tid":659040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五球可以買乜樓？！咪公屋囉！！！","createTime":"2018-05-09T13:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T01:01:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be8f5bd4d5f1611cb59996b8f26d9b10f3e31778","tid":659040,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:19:26.000Z","msg":"全港最貴公屋！李鄭屋邨賣538萬元<br />\n   <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/211919_79d922fae7bb665c44a1e4f8a38e8f02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F211919_79d922fae7bb665c44a1e4f8a38e8f02.png&h=ce66b68d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n居屋、夾屋連環出現樓王後，公屋樓價都再有突破。長沙灣公屋李鄭屋邨和睦樓中層16室，實用面積494方呎，以538萬元登記售出，創全港公屋成交金額新高，實用呎價10,891元。原業主2015年僅以240萬元購入，持貨短短3年，帳面賺298萬元，單位升值1.24倍。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，是次成交金額打破去年10月沙田公屋顯徑邨賣530萬元的舊紀錄。"},{"pid":"8719d1dc628db54847e77c0d18f8e2f24073cec8","tid":659040,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180509/photo/bkn-20180509163603401-0509_00842_001_02p.jpg?20180509211235\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180509163603401-0509_00842_001_02p.jpg%3F20180509211235&h=3b852837&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"983d363cafe194aa305132fee9014d92eadc3524","tid":659040,"uid":37037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"得公屋得天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21a0732c3ffe21d075376f85f33d5fb500966c5","tid":659040,"uid":41508,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9885a4ab26ae271c0d9e2513da79815b75119e34","tid":659040,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"麥公屋可以炒賣咩"},{"pid":"d96abda95af833fe667985778039e0